%F A188615 (Brocard angle) = arccot((a^2+b^2+c^2)/(4*area(ABC))) = arccot(sqrt(8)).
%F A188615 Also equals arcsin(1/3) or arccsc(3). - _Jean-Fran√ßois Alcover_, May 29 2013
